99
00:04:55.763 --> 00:04:59.500
MAN: Hey. check it.
bruv. Look at this one.

100
00:04:59.633 --> 00:05:02.536
<i>- NARRATOR: Crustaceans. marine
mammals. birds.</i> - (sighs)

101
00:05:02.636 --> 00:05:04.438
<i>turtles. anything that...</i>

102
00:05:04.538 --> 00:05:07.040
