192
00:09:36.744 --> 00:09:38.278
It's not quite the
same thing. but

193
00:09:38.378 --> 00:09:39.823
I'd rather have it and
not need it than need it

194
00:09:39.847 --> 00:09:41.457
- and not have it. you know?
- That's nice.

195
00:09:41.481 --> 00:09:42.826
