Anchorage. Alaska.

201
00:09:56.263 --> 00:09:57.396
Not a fan of the snow. huh?

202
00:09:57.397 --> 00:09:58.799
Not a fan of five
and a half hours

203
00:09:58.899 --> 00:10:00.333
