237
00:11:31.691 --> 00:11:34.160
At the time. his
lawyer was present.

238
00:11:34.161 --> 00:11:36.029
so the cameras were off.

239
00:11:36.163 --> 00:11:38.198
But once the FBI
entered his cell.

240
00:11:38.298 --> 00:11:39.832
